		</fdd:general>
		<fdd:history>
			<p>MBOXCL is so named because messages are distinguished not by &quot;From &quot; lines but rather by the &apos;Content-Length:&apos; (CL) header. </p>
			<p>MBOXCL and MBOXCL2 originated from the file format used by Unix System V Release 4 mail tools</p>
